lead_paragraph: Frenchman Alexander Levy will take a four-shot lead into Sunday's third and final round of the European Open after the tournament in Germany was reduced to 54 holes due to fog delays.

headline.print_headline: Frenchman Levy Stays Ahead in Fog-Hit European Open
